title: The First Ever Radio Hour 7/11/22
itunes:title: The First Ever Radio Hour 7/11/22
description:
On this weeks radio hour - Jeremy’s playing singles / tracks from new or upcoming albums! 

This episode includes tracks by Julien Baker, Alvvays, Young Guv, End, Bartees Strange, Alex G, Candy, Greet Death, Viagra Boys, Interpol, MUNA, Anthony Green and more!

Subscribe to the PATREON and receive a brand new radio hour every Sunday! Thats two additional episodes a month AND you get them a day early! You'll also see a complete list of songs played on this episode.

Follow the show on Instagram and Twitter!
